_sText:
This map is set in Prague, featuring a realistic depiction of the city. The map is largely unchanged from the original CS:GO version, apart from some visual downgrades made for performance reasons.

DISCLAIMER

There already exists a port of this map to CS: Source, however it's very poorly optimized and prone to frequent crashes. This version of the map fixes these issues and, in general, performs better than the other port.
